<ingredients><ingredient amount="0.25 Cup">Red Onion</ingredient><ingredient amount="2.0 Tablespoon">Juice</ingredient></ingredients>
<instructions>
Remove kernels from ears of corn.
In a medium bowl, toss together corn kernels, jalape&#241;o, onion, cilantro, lime juice, garlic, and salt.
Refrigerate until ready to serve.
</instructions>
